                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elementarfähigkeit</span></p><p>Verursacht 2 Pkt. <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo-SCH</span>, erschafft 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Generalbanner</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Generalbanner</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Kampfstatus</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo-SCH </span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 228, 217)\">durch deine Figur +1.</span><br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dauer (Runden): 2</span> (Max. Dauer: 3 Runden).</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/24/61142474/938b4e094906a85cee73a083091b261c_514166688730030136.png",
